<p>	Q.  Was that the longest few seconds of your life at the end after the free throw went in? </p>
<p>	Q.  What does this mean to you personally and talk about  what it means to the context of the whole university's athletic scene? </p>
<p>	Q.  Can you just explain what the three seniors have meant to the program, and also how competitive can you be without them?  What do you see ahead?</p>
<p>	Q.  And as far as next season without them? </p>
